address: Kalmia Rose | 9808 S Kalmia St, Los Angeles, CA
description:
Kalmia Rose Apartments is a brand new, mixed-income community in the historic Watts neighborhood of Southern Los Angeles. Located just one block from from Freedom Plaza Mall, new transit stops, and Jordan Downs Recreation Center, Kalmia Rose is the newest hub for modern, convenient living in South LA. 

Residents can enjoy onsite laundry lounges, a furnished community room, secured entry, bicycle parking, & more!

address: 10522 Lou Dillon Ave #10524, Los Angeles, CA 90002
description:
SECTION 8 WELCOMED. This recently renovated 2 bedroom 1. restroom unit has been updated with fresh paint, new kitchen/restroom modern cabinets, new kitchen/restroom fixtures, and updated flooring including tile throughout the rest of the unit. The bedrooms and the living room have ceiling fans to keep you cool on hot days; and a wall heater for cold days. Additionally, there are washer and dryer hookups and parking is available for one car. The property has security cameras (Eufy) around the premises. Microwave included.

1 year lease agreement term, owner pays pest control, lawn maintenance, and sewer. Tenant pays for gas, electricity, trash, and water.Hide

Welcome to your next home! This beautifully maintained 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom house located at 1947 E 114th Street offers comfort, convenience, and classic charm in a quiet neighborhood setting. Step inside to find a spacious living area filled with natural light, hardwood flooring, and a neutral color palette that suits any style. The updated kitchen features modern appliances, ample cabinet space, and room for a breakfast nook.

Each bedroom is generously sized with plenty of closet space, and the bathroom is clean and functional with updated fixtures. Enjoy a private backyard perfect for relaxing, entertaining, or gardening along with a full basement for extra storage or potential workspace.Hide

3bd, 1bth upstairs unit available in duplex. This extremely spacious unit comes with an even more spacious yard. This unit's natural light highlights the updated kitchen, open living room, and cozy bedrooms with closets. (SECTION 8 OK)

$35 credit check is required for each adult over the age of 18. 
AUGUST ONLY: $35 credit check fee to be credit to first month's rent with the signing of a 1 year lease!

Very walkable and friendly neighborhood:
 Grocery Store: 8 minute walk
 Planet Fitness: 5 minute walk
 Metro Green & Blue Lines: 5 minute walk
 Convenience, Eateries, etc: 5 - 10 minute walk

Our small and communicative management team is looking for a respectful family or group of occupants to work together in providing a safe and welcoming home environment.

1. Multiple rental agreement and lease options! (deposit and first month's rent due at signing)

2. No smoking in unit. Spacious yard available as an alternate. 

3. Pets: Please call for more info! 

4. FREE parking with the signing of a 1-year lease! (Proof of registration within the past 3 years is required)

5. Tenant is responsible for water and electricity.Hide
